\f1\b \cf2 CINNA THE POET\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf2 What is my name? Whither am I going? Where do I\
dwell? Am I a married man or a bachelor? Then, to\
answer every man directly and briefly, wisely and\
truly: wisely I say, I am a bachelor.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 Second Citizen\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf2 That's as much as to say, they are fools that marry:\
you'll bear me a bang for that, I fear. Proceed; directly.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 CINNA THE POET\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf2 Directly, I am going to Caesar's funeral.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 First Citizen\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

