Makes me forgetful?\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 BRUTUS\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \cf2 Yes, Cassius; and, from henceforth,\
When you are over-earnest with your Brutus,\
He'll think your mother chides, and leave you so.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

